name: AEX LEVERAGE
description: The AEX Leverage index tracks the performance of a strategy that has a multiple (2x) exposure to an underlying AEX index with the support of short-term financing. Suspended if the underlying index is less than 75% of close of previous day.

name: AEX XBEAR GR
description: The AEX XBear GR index tracks the performance of a strategy which reverses a multiple (-x2) exposure to the underlying index by combining a short position on the underlying AEX GR index and exposure to a risk-free money-market instrument, (the EONIA or other rate). The latter exposure consists of the money invested in the index plus the multiple (-x2) short positions. Suspended if the underlying index is greater than 125% of close of previous day.

name: AJAX
description: AFC Ajax is a soccer club. This group's activities are focused in soccer, marketing soccer-related items through sponsorships, television, merchandise sales.

name: AMSTERDAM COMMOD.
description: Amsterdam Commodities specializes in the trading and distribution of agricultural products and raw materials (dried fruits, spices, aromatic herbs and coconuts; Catz brand) for the food processing industry. The group also sells natural rubber to tire and shoe manufacturers and to the pharmaceutical industry.

name: BETER BED
description: Beter Bed Holding specializes in the distribution of bedroom products and equipment (furniture, mattresses, box springs, textiles, hospital mattress sales).

name: BEVER HOLDING
description: Bever Holding specializes in developing, owning, and managing real estate assets.

name: BOUSSARD GAVAUDAN
description: Founded in 2006, Boussard Gavaudan Holding is a closed investment company specializing in acquiring shares in alternative funds (primarily the Sark Fund), speculative funds, and venture-capital funds.

name: BRILL KON
description: Founded in 1683, Brill is a leading international academic publisher. The publications are related to Ancient Near East and Egypt, Middle East and Islamic studies, Asian studies (incl. Hotei imprint), classical studies, Medieval and Early Modern studies, biblical and religious studies, social sciences, biology, science (VSP imprint), human rights and Public International Law (Nijhoff imprint). In addition, Brill is a major provider of primary source materials online and on microform for researchers in the humanities and social sciences through its imprint IDC.

name: CTAC
description: Ctac is an IT services company specialized in the design, development and implementation of SAP systems (deployment and integration of specific applications, primarily logistical chain management and sales management, internet portals, etc.).

name: EASE2PAY NV
description: The business activities of DOCdata NV is a leading independent provider of supply chain management services for content owners and movie, audio, multimedia and software publishers in Europe. The group also provides e-Fulfilment, e-Financial, e-Commerce and e Partnership solutions to clients, and designs, builds and delivers production systems, which utilise optical and laser technology for application in amongst others document security systems for high security printers and equipment for processing of packaging materials.

name: HAL TRUST
description: HAL Trust is an investment company. Income breaks down by activity as follows: portfolio management, real estate asset development and management, currency investments.

name: HOLLAND COLOURS
description: Founded in 1979, Holland Colours specializes in the manufacturing of pigments and coloring preparations for the construction and public works, packaging and chemical industries: concentrated pigments (intense coloring of thermoplastics, particularly for water, beer and cosmetics bottles), lexible PVC coloring (toys, balls, routing mats, Holcoflex), colored powders (coloring for industrial paint and plastics, PVC plates and sections and roofing).

name: HUNTER DOUGLAS
description: Hunter Douglas is the world leader in the design, manufacturing and marketing of blinds (vertical and horizontal blinds, Persian, Venetian, or rolling blinds, shutters, solar protectors, etc. sold under the following brands: HunterDouglas, Luxaflex, Flexalum, Sunway, Sunflex, and Comfortex). The group also manufactures and sells architectural products (aluminum ceilings and ready-to-use foam walls, covering systems, soundproofing, Luxalon brand).

name: HUNTER DOUGLAS
description: Hunter Douglas is the world leader in the design, manufacturing and marketing of blinds (vertical and horizontal blinds, Persian, Venetian, or rolling blinds, shutters, solar protectors, etc. sold under the following brands: HunterDouglas, Luxaflex, Flexalum, Sunway, Sunflex, and Comfortex). The group also manufactures and sells architectural products (aluminum ceilings and ready-to-use foam walls, covering systems, soundproofing, Luxalon brand).

name: ICT GROUP
description: ICT Automatisering is the Netherlands top integrated software development and marketing company. The Group sells integrated software for video equipment manufacturers (DVD players, digital TV) and mobile communications (telephones, wireless accessories), automotive equipment (radios, navigation systems), semi-conductors and medical equipment (diagnostic, control, imaging equipment).

name: KENDRION
description: Kendrion specializes in the design, manufacturing, and marketing of automotive (plastic and metal components used mainly in security systems) and mechanical (electromagnetic systems and components designed for use in the production of elevators, clasps, industrial robots, control and dialysis equipment). The group also distributes plastic semi-finished products.

name: NEDAP

name: NEWAYS ELECTRONICS
description: Neways Electronics International is an international one-stop-provider of advanced integrated components, assemblies and systems, offering solutions for the development, engineering, testing and manufacture of small to medium high-tech and high-quality batches of (micro-) electronics, printed circuit boards (PCBs) and cables into complete electronic box-built systems.

name: ORANJEWOUD A

The company also has a division focusing on temporary employment in the same working areas. Activities: consulting and engineering services, engineering project execution, temporary employment.

name: PORCELEYNE FLES

name: STERN GROEP

Holdings and Stern Beheer in 2000, Stern Groep is a automobile distributor: a network of 50 multi-brand concessions, notably Mercedes-Benz, BMW, Alfa Romeo, Opel/General Motors, Ford and Renault; operates 14 gas stations on the outskirts of Amsterdam and in the southern part of the Netherlands; repair of damaged vehicles (9 garages), car hire (3 800 cars), management of car fleets, fitting out interiors of company cars.

name: BELRECA

name: FLORIDIENNE

It offers KeyPay, an open and platform-independent electronic payment solution for use in e-cash, debit, credit, and e-purse applications; Key-Shopper, a software for customer loyalty services, which provides open and modular electronic card solutions; and Key-Identity, an application for electronic identification solutions that could be used in private network environments and public identification applications, including identity cards, drivers licenses, and passports.
